method: York Colleges Guild Dinner Day Doubles
footnotes: Rung prior to Evensong as part of the service ringing.
The variation 16vu (Reverse Bob with Grandsire Plains) is rung for the first time. The band would like to name this variation "York Colleges Guild Dinner Day".
Not rung on the York Colleges Guild Dinner Day, but named so that we can ring a whole quarter in the variation when it comes to it.
